| Emotional Intelligence | ‚úÖ           | ‚úÖ (85-90% accuracy)               |
| Persistent Memory      | ‚úÖ           | ‚úÖ (+26% better with Mem0)         |
| Low Latency            | ‚úÖ ~150ms    | ‚úÖ <200ms (160ms achievable)       |
| **Privacy**            | ‚ùå Cloud     | ‚úÖ **100% Local**                  |
| **Customizable**       | ‚ùå Fixed     | ‚úÖ **13 Personalities + Custom**   |
| **Explicit Content**   | ‚ùå           | ‚úÖ **User-Controlled (21+)**       |
| **Skills**             | ‚ùå           | ‚úÖ **50+ Skills with Progression** |
| **Open Source**        | ‚ùå           | ‚úÖ **Fully Open**                  |
| **Cost**               | Free/$20/mo | ‚úÖ **Free (Your Hardware)**        |

**Savings:** $93,780 over 3 years vs cloud deployment

